;These profiles have the potential to interfere with your life offline, and can contribute to unfair practices by being improperly used for price discrimination, decreased creditworthiness, more expensive insurance coverage or unfavorable employment or health reports.
Re taq ruwäch b'i'aj re' yetikïr ye'ok pan ak'aslem toq man at k'o ta pa k'amab'ey, chuqa' yetikïr nikib'än tz'ilanel taq samaj toq man pa rub'eyal ta ye'okisäx richin kisamajixik taq ajil, ruch'utinisaxik tojïk, ruq'ijul tok'aslemal jotöl rajil o rutzijol samaj o itzel raxnaqil.


